@uri = http://localhost:9006/api/v1/water-prices
@keycloak=http://localhost:8080/realms/cmsn/protocol/openid-connect
@client_secret=

### get token
POST {{keycloak}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Accept: application/json

grant_type=password&
client_id=&
client_secret={{client_secret}}&
username=&
password=&
scope=openid

> {%
  client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
  client.global.set("refresh_token", response.body.refresh_token);
%}

### C
### Case 1: Tạo mới bảng giá nước thành công
POST {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usageTarget": "DOMESTIC",
  "tax": 5.0,
  "environmentPrice": 1000.00,
  "applicationPeriod": "2024-01-01",
  "expirationDate": "2024-12-31",
  "description": "Giá nước sinh hoạt năm 2024"
}

### Case 2: Tạo thất bại - Thiếu thông tin bắt buộc (usageTarget, tax)
POST {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "environmentPrice": 1000.00,
  "applicationPeriod": "2024-01-01"
}

### Case 3: Tạo thất bại - Giá trị âm không hợp lệ (tax < 0)
POST {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usageTarget": "INDUSTRIAL",
  "tax": -1.0,
  "environmentPrice": 2000.00,
  "applicationPeriod": "2024-01-01",
  "expirationDate": "2024-12-31"
}

### Case 4: Tạo thất bại - Không hợp lệ format ngày tháng
POST {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usageTarget": "COMMERCIAL",
  "tax": 10.0,
  "environmentPrice": 1500.00,
  "applicationPeriod": "01-01-2024",
  "expirationDate": "2024/12/31"
}

### U
@priceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-B00000000001

### Case 1: Cập nhật thành công
PUT {{uri}}/{{priceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usageTarget": "DOMESTIC",
  "tax": 8.0,
  "description": "Giá nước sinh hoạt năm 2024 (Đã điều chỉnh thuế)"
}

### Case 2: Cập nhật thất bại - ID không tồn tại
PUT {{uri}}/invalid-uuid-price
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tax": 10.0
}

### D
### Case 1: Xóa thành công
DELETE {{uri}}/{{priceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Case 2: Xóa thất bại - ID không tồn tại
DELETE {{uri}}/invalid-price-id
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### R
### get all, missing all params
GET {{uri}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### get all, pageable
GET {{uri}}?page=0&size=15
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### get all, filter
GET {{uri}}?keyword=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### get all, filter
GET {{uri}}?keyword=2025-10-10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### get all, pageable and filter
GET {{uri}}?page=0&size=15&keyword=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### Lấy chi tiết theo ID
GET {{uri}}/{{priceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
